32.000Z","msg":"（緊急）點解之前死都唔肯停課，昨天停曬八大，之後就暴力清場，好明顯政府認為滅左你大學生，事件就會完，其它大學都要準備徹離<br />\n對無人性的林鄭來說，唔好誤以為停課係為你地安全着想，佢係想暴力清場。<br />\n仲有，有消息內地生徹走，好明顯為屠殺鋪路<br />\n必須推上國際，要話比世界聽&ldquo;天安門事件&rdquo;又即將發生，仲要係警察想走入八大，消滅整個世代的大學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712238</a>"},{"pid":"850801b696bc5430d55743c61e87b26d4f8ab5d3","tid":1712333,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2046c6b99229272f0eec9ba5af4e17172270ae9","tid":1712333,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"水砲車啲水係溝通用口水嘅延伸?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"留意返，佢成條液柱射落個火到，射完之後竟然仲大火咗<br />\n代表乜? 即係佢啲液體係助燃<br />\n水又點會助燃?"},{"pid":"15d1a4df116767ce40de89a42146d526624b396f","tid":1712333,"uid":29424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"黑警淨係識講大話！！！已經射緊水砲DKLM !!"},{"pid":"3aa0a90dc989e9e8051979fc2cdf33fd654c74c9","tid":1712333,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"咁黑警自己走咪得囉 講咩野姐"},{"pid":"9680f979e51e4cfbef18059855dc6b6cdc71d46e","tid":1712333,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"335e76aa5594dc3ad1d287baded91ee3ecf3a0ee","tid":1712333,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"！！！中大告急，中大告急！！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出唔到去嘅人</span></span>幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7R%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=54b099b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n今日Task分類<br />\n/task1: 中環罷工<br />\n/task2: 其他中國同香港議題<br />\n<span s